longBusinessSummary: Item 9 Labs Corp. operates as a vertically integrated cannabis operator and dispensary franchisor in the United States. The company produces cannabis and cannabis-related products in various categories, such as flower; concentrates; distillates; and hardware. It offers products through licensed dispensaries to consumers in Arizona. The company is headquartered in Phoenix, Arizona.
